println("  | 25| Σμ(n/d)·d = φ(n) (Möbius)     | verified 6 test n's      | ⭐    |")
println("  | +| σ/φ = n (unique to n=6)        | 12/2 = 6                 | ⭐    |")
println("")
println("  All valid identities PASS assertions")
